===蘋果公司的商標===
[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]的商標有時會被誤認為是源於圖靈自殺时咬下的半個蘋果<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/media/logos-that-became-legends-icons-from-the-world-of-advertising-768077.html|title = Logos that became legends: Icons from the world of advertising|work = The Independent|publisher = www.independent.co.uk|accessdate = 2009-09-14|location = London|date = 2008-01-04|archive-date = 2009-10-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091003003651/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/media/logos-that-became-legends-icons-from-the-world-of-advertising-768077.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>，但該圖案的设计师<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://creativebits.org/interview/interview_rob_janoff_designer_apple_logo |title = Interview with Rob Janoff, designer of the Apple logo |publisher = creativebits |accessdate = 2009-09-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171024013734/http://creativebits.org/interview/interview_rob_janoff_designer_apple_logo |archive-date = 2017-10-24 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>和蘋果公司都否認了這一說法<ref>{{Harvnb|Leavitt|2007|p=280}}</ref>。而公司创办人[[史蒂夫·賈伯斯|史蒂夫·賈伯斯]]在接受[[史蒂芬·弗莱|史蒂芬·弗莱]]问到此事时说：“上帝啊，我们希望它（LOGO向圖靈致敬）是真的。但它只是巧合。”（''"God we wish it were. It's just a coincidence."''）<ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20120620-the-turing-test-of-time |title = "Science & Environment - Alan Turing: Separating the man and the myth" |work = [[BBC|BBC]] |date = 2012-06-21 |accessdate = 2012-06-23 |archive-date = 2012-06-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120623064706/http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20120620-the-turing-test-of-time |dead-url = no }}</ref>

